{"tid":2152664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門市廣場業主迫害黃店,威迫其24小時內搬走民主女神像,否則派人硬闖搬走","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:13:40.000Z","uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6000df7eda38646e16091d064122e0da39eaa93e","tid":2152664,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰】屯門市廣場指放民主女神像違約 告Chickeeduck限24小時移除否則入店處置<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2F6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=3b424d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2F6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE%2F&h=f94a839d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE/</a><br />\n<br />\n連鎖童裝店Chickeeduck早前在荃灣愉景新城分店擺放香港「民主女神像」，遭商場要求移走雕像，業主其後拒絕續租。Chickeeduck早前再在屯門市廣場分店擺放女神像，遭業主入稟高院，指控違反租約，要求法庭頒令強制該店24小時內移走雕像，否則業主有權進場處置。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA1344/20】"},{"pid":"401abe1f9d4297aad672e3a2c3700b65cb2a5c89","tid":2152664,"uid":212884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b3af1d1c07362e22cf585512b1848de21e54c0a","tid":2152664,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a575e72405c73b2bd06c3f3f0e8121c5970d9d3","tid":2152664,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"708167ec2a1f7716c76c082ff3cd4685e32b9193","tid":2152664,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"Ok, 等法庭判左先囉"}]}